<li id="cite_note-independence-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-independence_9-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKabzińska1998" class="citation journal cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source">Kabzińska, Krystyna (1998). "<i>Chemiczne i polskie aspekty odkrycia polonu i radu</i>" &#91;Chemical and Polish Aspects of Polonium and Radium Discovery&#93;. <i>Przemysł Chemiczny (The Chemical Industry)</i> (in Polish). <b>77</b>: 104–107.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Przemys%C5%82+Chemiczny+%28The+Chemical+Industry%29&amp;rft.atitle=Chemiczne+i+polskie+aspekty+odkrycia+polonu+i+radu&amp;rft.volume=77&amp;rft.pages=104-107&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.aulast=Kabzi%C5%84ska&amp;rft.aufirst=Krystyna&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarie+Curie" class="Z3988"></span></span>
